reviews.review_text: shed a tear everytime I usually cry during Jerry's emotional soloing in Scarlet, especially after the long awaited Unbroken Chain...he is trying so hard, with his health so bad at this point in his career....I remember he looked like a white ghost and an old man at these shows ( I was there for 3/22...best Foolish Heart all time, btw;)....such a sad thing to know he was only 52 here, and died a few days after his 53rd...great jams here for 1995 (4 stars for the show)
